        <h2>The starting point</h2>
        <p><blockquote>There is a fine line between truth and lie, love and hate, good and evil. Our beliefs decide where we stand; after all, our ancestors used to say that no two people are the same.</blockquote></p>
        <p>Avalon had always been a mystery to me. For a kid who lived for stories that took her to different worlds, Avalon was everything that I could dream of. As I grew up, my thought process changed, but my curiosity never died, and it gave me a push to dive deeper into the stories that revolved around this mythical place that, according to some, still existsâ€”always hidden from the eyes of us normal humans.</p>
